1
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:33,280
Smile! Give me a smile!

2
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:54,240
You haven't come since school started.

3
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:55,880
You've missed so many classes.

4
00:00:57,079 --> 00:00:57,840
At this rate,

5
00:00:58,679 --> 00:01:00,119
did I really get in for nothing?

6
00:01:01,039 --> 00:01:02,679
That manager of yours is way out of line.

7
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,000
At this stage in your life,

8
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,319
you should focus on studying.

9
00:01:05,439 --> 00:01:06,760
You can't lose sight of the big picture.

10
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,319
Exactly.

11
00:01:09,159 --> 00:01:10,359
You have to learn to say no.

12
00:01:15,599 --> 00:01:16,280
Excuse me.

13
00:01:20,079 --> 00:01:22,840
Gui Fang, aren't you going to introduce him?

14
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:25,719
How did he manage to

15
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:27,799
blend in with us so naturally?

16
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:29,519
Are you really Wei Mingtian?

17
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:32,280
Are you really Wei Mingtian in the flesh?

18
00:01:33,159 --> 00:01:34,040
Yes, yes, yes.

19
00:01:34,959 --> 00:01:35,400
This is

20
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:38,079
the comrade-in-arms who got into college with me.

21
00:01:38,439 --> 00:01:39,159
Wei Mingtian.

22
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:41,799
That's right.

23
00:01:42,239 --> 00:01:42,959
Comrades-in-arms.

24
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:44,400
Comrades-in-arms.

25
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:49,000
Alright, alright. Eat up, eat up.

26
00:01:49,719 --> 00:01:50,359
Eat some more.

27
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,000
Let me hold that for you.

28
00:01:59,239 --> 00:01:59,760
No need, no need.

29
00:02:00,079 --> 00:02:00,719
It's pretty dirty.

30
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:01,599
I'll hold it myself.

31
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,879
You have fieldwork classes this early?

32
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:05,599
Yeah.

33
00:02:06,079 --> 00:02:08,599
And I was the first in our group to grow seedlings.

34
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,719
What does our school greenhouse look like?

35
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:12,960
Can I go see it?

36
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:16,159
Part of it should be open to visitors.

37
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:17,919
I'll ask the teacher for you later.

38
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,120
But not today.

39
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,759
The student council has meetings these days.

40
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:21,560
It's pretty busy.

41
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:24,159
The day after tomorrow. If you're free then,

42
00:02:24,159 --> 00:02:25,560
I should be able to show you around.

43
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:28,400
Gui Fang.

44
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:31,280
You seem to be living such a fulfilling life.

45
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,759
Quite fulfilling.

46
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,599
I'm in a rush to get to the greenhouse up ahead.

47
00:02:37,599 --> 00:02:38,599
I can't chat right now.

48
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:40,120
Let's catch up later. Bye.

49
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,439
But why do I feel like

50
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,360
you're drifting further and further away from me?

51
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,439
Rui Rui

52
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:03,680
Were you waiting for me?

53
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:05,479
Auntie

54
00:03:06,199 --> 00:03:07,360
Don't call me Auntie. Don't call me Auntie.

55
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:09,639
Gui Fang

56
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:10,879
Auntie

57
00:03:11,639 --> 00:03:12,759
Just call me Gui Fang.

58
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:14,479
Gui Fang

59
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,879
My mind is still blank right now.

60
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:20,000
You and Xiaocan kept this from everyone.

61
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,919
Is there a reason you couldn't tell us?

62
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:27,479
Actually, about this...

63
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:28,960
The doctor warned me...

64
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,319
that I absolutely couldn't tell anyone.

65
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,159
But I believe...

66
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:32,800
you definitely wouldn't hurt Xiaocan.

67
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:34,120
Come here, let me tell you.

68
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,400
This medicine...

69
00:03:38,719 --> 00:03:39,960
was stolen by Xiaocan.

70
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:42,400
Stolen?

71
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:44,800
Look at the effect on me now.

72
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,800
It was purely by accident.

73
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:47,759
I don't know what happened either.

74
00:03:47,759 --> 00:03:48,919
I just turned into this.

75
00:03:49,159 --> 00:03:49,879
But this matter...

76
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,199
if anyone else finds out...

77
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:52,840
Xiaocan could very likely get arrested.

78
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,159
And go to jail.

79
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,199
I understand.

80
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:58,919
I can understand...

81
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:01,319
why Xiaocan didn't tell me the truth.

82
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:03,840
But I can't accept...

83
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,639
that he treated me like a burden to be thrown away...

84
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:06,360
when he broke up with me.

85
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:07,719
No, no, no.

86
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:08,879
That's not what he meant.

87
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,439
Xiaocan... But that's just what he did.

88
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:11,759
Gui Fang.

89
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,120
I came today...

90
00:04:13,759 --> 00:04:15,120
just to clear things up with you.

91
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,399
When it comes to feelings...

92
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:19,560
I hope...

93
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,879
it's something Xiaocan and I solve together.

94
00:04:23,839 --> 00:04:24,879
But that kid Xiaocan...

95
00:04:24,879 --> 00:04:26,720
he really likes you a lot.

96
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:27,839
I know.

97
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:30,399
But a relationship isn't just about liking someone.

98
00:04:31,199 --> 00:04:31,800
Don't you think?

99
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:39,920
Anyway...

100
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,839
I will handle this properly with Xiaocan.

101
00:04:43,079 --> 00:04:43,920
You can rest assured.

102
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,639
I'll go to class now.

103
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,319
Okay, okay, go ahead.

104
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:01,439
That's great.

105
00:05:03,319 --> 00:05:05,600
How old is she? So mature.

106
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,759
Rui Jie

107
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:21,839
Where's Kong Xiaocan?

108
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,279
You're actually coming to find him yourself?

109
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,600
Did you two make up?

110
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:27,240
I want to talk to him.

111
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:27,920
Talk?

112
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:28,560
Talking is good.

113
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,120
He's working right now.

114
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,279
I'll send you his address.

115
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,240
Thanks.

116
00:05:39,639 --> 00:05:41,800
How many jobs does he actually work in a day?

117
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:42,920
A lot.

118
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,360
I don't know where he is right now either.

119
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,920
Anyway, contact him before you go.

120
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:47,720
Have a good talk, Rui Jie.

121
00:05:51,439 --> 00:05:52,639
Hello, here is your dish.

122
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:53,480
Thank you.

123
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,120
Enjoy your meal.

124
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:23,439
Has he been living like this all year?

125
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:33,199
I can only say it's been much harder than this.

126
00:08:06,439 --> 00:08:07,160
I'm not going back.

127
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,160
Where are you running? Where are you running?

128
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,920
We agreed I could attend classes at school this week.

129
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:10,639
Class is over now.

130
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:11,800
I didn't take up your study time.

131
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,160
Everyone is studying.

132
00:08:13,399 --> 00:08:14,480
Their lives are so fulfilling.

133
00:08:14,639 --> 00:08:15,959
I... I want the same.

134
00:08:15,959 --> 00:08:17,480
Do you know if you refuse this job...

135
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,319
how much we'll have to pay in damages?

136
00:08:19,879 --> 00:08:20,560
Don't push me.

137
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:21,600
Push me too hard and I'll terminate the contract with you.

138
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,439
The termination fee will ruin you.

139
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:26,759
Let's go.

140
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,160
Go.

141
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,240
Should've just listened earlier.

142
00:08:43,639 --> 00:08:44,320
I didn't get in!

143
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:46,159
I didn't get in! Stop the car!

144
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,159
Stop the car!

145
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:48,399
Stop the car!

146
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:01,000
It's not that I won't let you play.

147
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,080
No, wait.

148
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,720
It's not that I won't let you go to school.

149
00:09:04,879 --> 00:09:06,000
It's normal to be obsessed with studying.

150
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,759
I can understand that.

151
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:07,120
But...

152
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:09,080
You have to understand work-life balance, right?

153
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:11,039
You can't just go to school forever.

154
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,120
Can you spend your whole life...

155
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,399
...just studying like this?

156
00:09:13,519 --> 00:09:14,559
You still have to work eventually.

157
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:16,440
You can't let the important stuff get delayed.

158
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:17,240
Let me tell you.

159
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,960
I hope I'm wrong more than anyone else.

160
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:19,879
But this is reality.

161
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:21,759
This is the most suitable and only path for you.

162
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:22,279
Do you understand?

163
00:09:22,519 --> 00:09:23,399
Speak up. Ignoring me?

164
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:24,840
Not convinced?

165
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,279
How about this.

166
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,039
This time...

167
00:09:29,279 --> 00:09:30,679
if you do a good job on this work...

168
00:09:32,759 --> 00:09:34,120
and get good traffic...

169
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,240
I'll reward you with two sets of exam papers.

170
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:43,960
Really.

171
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:46,840
I keep my word.

172
00:09:50,799 --> 00:09:51,279
Alright.

173
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:54,720
And you.

174
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,039
Is everyone here? Why are you driving?

175
00:09:56,039 --> 00:09:57,279
Why don't you two just go off on your own?

176
00:09:58,039 --> 00:09:58,799
So annoying.

177
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:03,120
Let me tell you.

178
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:04,799
What we're filming this time is a...

179
00:10:04,799 --> 00:10:05,919
romance-themed commercial.

180
00:10:06,039 --> 00:10:08,000
Basically, we're shooting in this amusement park.

181
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,080
As for the content...

182
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,399
it's you and a young lady...

183
00:10:10,399 --> 00:10:11,919
going on exciting rides together.

184
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:13,720
You... just have fun with it.

185
00:10:20,519 --> 00:10:20,919
How about it?

186
00:10:23,679 --> 00:10:24,159
Is she pretty?

187
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:28,360
That...

188
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:29,080
Is it exciting?

189
00:10:30,039 --> 00:10:30,559
Exciting.

190
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:31,679
Want to play?

191
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,720
I'll let you play until you puke later.

192
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:34,240
Okay.

193
00:10:34,919 --> 00:10:35,480
Go get ready.

194
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,039
I'll go take care of something.

195
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,320
Tian.

196
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,039
I just spoke with the director.

197
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,039
This is our last take.

198
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:45,360
We wrap as soon as we finish.

199
00:10:45,639 --> 00:10:46,000
Is that okay?

200
00:10:46,919 --> 00:10:47,200
Come here.

201
00:10:55,919 --> 00:10:56,639
Don't swallow. Spit it out.

202
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,159
What's wrong with you?

203
00:10:59,159 --> 00:11:00,399
You don't need to save that mouthful.

204
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,320
By the way, Mike.

205
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,600
I want to invite my classmate to play here.

206
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,960
Can you help me buy two tickets?

207
00:11:12,639 --> 00:11:13,320
Is there a discount?

208
00:11:13,639 --> 00:11:14,679
What classmate?

209
00:11:14,679 --> 00:11:15,360
Didn't I tell you...

210
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:17,159
to stay away from those civilians?

211
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,399
It's my neighbor.

212
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,039
And my classmate.

213
00:11:20,559 --> 00:11:21,639
Who usually takes good care of me.

214
00:11:21,919 --> 00:11:23,480
She always lets me eat at her house for free.

215
00:11:23,559 --> 00:11:24,519
So what if you eat for free?

216
00:11:24,759 --> 00:11:25,559
No, wait, you...

217
00:11:26,039 --> 00:11:27,120
So what if you eat her food for free?

218
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:28,320
You're a star.

219
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:30,559
It's her honor that you eat a couple of meals at her house.

220
00:11:30,879 --> 00:11:32,200
Neighbors, classmates...

221
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:33,960
how did you get mixed up with them?

222
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:36,240
I just want to invite them here to have some fun.

223
00:11:36,639 --> 00:11:37,679
Just to thank them.

224
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,080
No.

225
00:11:39,639 --> 00:11:40,039
Xiao Tian.

226
00:11:40,399 --> 00:11:41,639
We're ready to shoot another take over there.

227
00:11:41,639 --> 00:11:42,279
Are you okay here?

228
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:45,879
I can't do it.

229
00:11:49,679 --> 00:11:50,639
He can, he can, he can.

230
00:11:50,679 --> 00:11:51,440
I can't do it anymore.

231
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:52,559
You...

232
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:55,000
Can you do it or not, Xiao Tian?

233
00:12:00,559 --> 00:12:01,639
Fine, I'll get you the tickets.

234
00:12:04,639 --> 00:12:05,320
I can do it again.

235
00:12:05,559 --> 00:12:05,960
Fine.

236
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,440
Then get ready, we'll shoot another one.

237
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:09,320
Thanks, Mike.

238
00:12:09,759 --> 00:12:10,200
Shoot well.

239
00:12:10,919 --> 00:12:11,639
I'll go get you the tickets.

240
00:12:11,759 --> 00:12:13,080
This kid is growing up too fast.

241
00:12:25,519 --> 00:12:28,080
I was supposed to retire in a few years.

242
00:12:28,799 --> 00:12:31,159
Why do I have to suffer like this here?

243
00:12:31,799 --> 00:12:32,399
Junior.

244
00:12:33,919 --> 00:12:34,919
Why is it you again?

245
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:37,960
Do you have work?

246
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,080
That you need me to finish for you?

247
00:12:42,159 --> 00:12:42,840
If not...

248
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,440
I'm going to finish my own work.

249
00:12:44,919 --> 00:12:45,279
You carry on.

250
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:53,200
This kid is growing up pretty fast.

251
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,840
I can go home early tonight.

252
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:01,919
Son.

253
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,519
Mom's making steamed pork today.

254
00:13:04,679 --> 00:13:06,320
There'll be a late-night snack for you after work.

255
00:13:12,519 --> 00:13:13,799
Brother Wang, you... you're tired today.

256
00:13:13,799 --> 00:13:14,639
Have another bowl.

257
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:15,399
Okay.

258
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:27,360
Sorry.

259
00:13:27,559 --> 00:13:28,200
We're closing.

260
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:47,480
Kong Xiaocan.

261
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:49,960
How many grates did you burn today?

262
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:50,600
Two.

263
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,559
If you don't watch the grates properly tomorrow...

264
00:13:52,559 --> 00:13:53,120
I'll dock your pay.

265
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,120
Lock the door in a bit.

266
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:00,399
My partner.

267
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,279
Is the partner tired?

268
00:14:11,679 --> 00:14:14,080
Occasional disputes are inevitable.

269
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:15,799
But it's also normal.

270
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:17,240
That's business.

271
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:18,559
Once you become partners...

272
00:14:18,559 --> 00:14:19,639
You just gang up to deceive people.

273
00:14:19,639 --> 00:14:20,039
Yes.

274
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:26,399
After locking up...

275
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,440
Are you going to see other partners?

276
00:14:29,799 --> 00:14:30,240
No need.

277
00:14:31,399 --> 00:14:32,159
Then let's talk.

278
00:14:38,879 --> 00:14:41,360
Are you very angry with me?

279
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,399
These past few days...

280
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:46,519
I've been thinking about it too.

281
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:48,559
If I were you...

282
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:49,879
What would I do?

283
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,440
Mom gets sick...

284
00:14:56,519 --> 00:14:59,159
The family burden suddenly falls on you.

285
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:01,159
