575
00:26:12,279 --> 00:26:13,279
Her friends are my friends

576
00:26:13,279 --> 00:26:14,559
We count as friends from now on

577
00:26:14,559 --> 00:26:15,359
Xiao Xi, don't be so polite

578
00:26:17,279 --> 00:26:18,279
My name is Xiao Yin

579
00:26:18,599 --> 00:26:19,519
Isn't your name Xu Xi?

580
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:21,640
Xu... Xu Xi didn't come

581
00:26:21,759 --> 00:26:22,759
I'm Chen Xiaoyin

582
00:26:25,039 --> 00:26:25,400
Right

583
00:26:26,359 --> 00:26:27,519
Gui Fang mentions you all the time

584
00:26:28,319 --> 00:26:28,839
I remembered wrong

585
00:26:29,440 --> 00:26:30,039
Xiao Yin, Xiao Yin

586
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:36,680
I'm alive again

587
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:38,319
I could go for another round

588
00:26:38,839 --> 00:26:39,400
Let's go, Cousin

589
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:42,599
Cousin, what's wrong?

590
00:26:43,119 --> 00:26:44,000
Are you not feeling well?

591
00:26:44,039 --> 00:26:44,640
I'm fine, I'm fine

592
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:45,279
Let me fan you

593
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:46,680
Let me massage your shoulders

594
00:26:46,839 --> 00:26:48,000
Is she not feeling well? Stay away from her

595
00:26:48,319 --> 00:26:50,200
Xiaocan, help me pick some more photos

596
00:26:50,200 --> 00:26:51,039
Which one do you think?

597
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:55,640
Cousin, I'd better fan you

598
00:26:57,039 --> 00:26:58,319
What is going on with you two?

599
00:26:58,480 --> 00:26:59,839
Cousin isn't feeling well

600
00:26:59,960 --> 00:27:01,440
You really don't know how to treat a lady

601
00:27:01,519 --> 00:27:02,920
There are plenty of people to care for her, she doesn't need you

602
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:04,519
It's fine, it's fine

603
00:27:05,119 --> 00:27:06,240
It's just my first time on this

604
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:07,680
I just need to rest a bit and I'll be fine

605
00:27:07,799 --> 00:27:08,799
Why don't you eat something sweet?

606
00:27:09,079 --> 00:27:10,240
I know, I know where they sell some

607
00:27:10,240 --> 00:27:11,119
I'll go buy it for you right now

608
00:27:11,279 --> 00:27:12,079
Let's go, brother, come with me

609
00:27:13,160 --> 00:27:13,799
Something sweet, right?

610
00:27:16,559 --> 00:27:17,960
Fang'er, what did they go do?

611
00:27:18,519 --> 00:27:19,200
To buy things

612
00:27:19,319 --> 00:27:20,119
Then I'll go help

613
00:27:20,119 --> 00:27:20,799
They can't carry it all

614
00:27:23,440 --> 00:27:25,720
Xiao Rui, why don't you go with them?

615
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:27,960
Can you sports students not eat sweets?

616
00:27:28,319 --> 00:27:29,160
You go buy something else

617
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:32,039
Okay

618
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:42,519
Tian

619
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:44,960
Why are you back?

620
00:27:45,319 --> 00:27:45,839
Take good care of her.

621
00:27:46,480 --> 00:27:47,279
Take care of yourself.

622
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:48,759
Alright, go on.

623
00:27:57,319 --> 00:27:58,240
Are you okay, Gui Fang?

624
00:27:59,519 --> 00:28:00,039
I'm fine.

625
00:28:00,480 --> 00:28:01,559
How about you? You okay?

626
00:28:01,799 --> 00:28:02,359
I'm alright.

627
00:28:02,680 --> 00:28:03,160
That's good.

628
00:28:04,079 --> 00:28:05,200
Actually, if it weren't for Li Wai...

629
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:06,880
hovering in front of me just now,

630
00:28:07,559 --> 00:28:09,240
I could've gone for another round.

631
00:28:11,519 --> 00:28:12,160
You're amazing.

632
00:28:12,279 --> 00:28:13,480
Why don't we take a break?

633
00:28:13,720 --> 00:28:14,720
Then go for another round.

634
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:16,400
Ride it one more time.

635
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:17,640
Can you handle it?

636
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:19,799
Sure.

637
00:28:20,359 --> 00:28:21,640
I can, I can.

638
00:28:22,599 --> 00:28:24,279
You don't look like you can handle it.

639
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:26,599
Let me see.

640
00:28:29,400 --> 00:28:30,839
How about this one? Is this okay?

641
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:32,480
This one looks like it changes colors.

642
00:28:32,759 --> 00:28:33,680
I haven't ridden it either.

643
00:28:33,680 --> 00:28:34,160
This is good, this is good.

644
00:28:34,160 --> 00:28:34,799
This is good, right?

645
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:35,279
Let's do this one.

646
00:28:35,279 --> 00:28:35,960
Then let's go ride this one.

647
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:36,480
Okay.

648
00:28:36,519 --> 00:28:37,359
Let's go line up first.

649
00:28:37,599 --> 00:28:39,079
Let's go. I'll message them in a bit.

650
00:28:39,599 --> 00:28:40,400
I'll get the cousin's share.

651
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:41,079
Don't fight over it.

652
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:41,759
We don't need you to.

653
00:28:42,440 --> 00:28:43,319
You better behave yourself.

654
00:28:43,519 --> 00:28:44,480
No, what are you doing?

655
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:46,720
I...

656
00:28:50,039 --> 00:28:51,319
No, Rui, what's with you two?

657
00:28:51,319 --> 00:28:52,799
Why are you targeting me like this?

658
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:54,599
I just like the cousin.

659
00:28:54,599 --> 00:28:56,119
I haven't done anything terrible.

660
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:58,000
You said you two broke up.

661
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,680
And you won't let me be happy? Seriously.

662
00:29:00,160 --> 00:29:02,920
Trust us, it's really for your own good.

663
00:29:10,920 --> 00:29:11,599
Xiaocan.

664
00:29:12,640 --> 00:29:14,240
Have the three of you known each other long?

665
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:16,519
A long time.

666
00:29:18,279 --> 00:29:18,640
So...

667
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:19,839
Um...

668
00:29:20,839 --> 00:29:23,200
Are you and Xu Rui dating?

669
00:29:44,359 --> 00:29:44,920
I see.

670
00:29:46,559 --> 00:29:47,319
We used to be.

671
00:29:51,799 --> 00:29:52,519
But we can only be...

672
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:00,160
Hurry up, hurry up.

673
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:01,559
The cousin's gonna get low blood sugar soon.

674
00:30:01,559 --> 00:30:02,039
Can you guys hurry up?

675
00:30:02,039 --> 00:30:03,599
I'm warning you, stay away from her.

676
00:30:03,599 --> 00:30:04,880
Or I'll feed you to the pendulum ride, hear me?

677
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:06,319
You just don't know how to care for people.

678
00:30:06,559 --> 00:30:07,839
The fireworks show is starting soon.

679
00:30:07,839 --> 00:30:09,200
The best time to confess.

680
00:30:09,599 --> 00:30:10,160
Stop dawdling.

681
00:30:10,160 --> 00:30:10,799
Hurry, hurry, hurry.

682
00:30:10,799 --> 00:30:12,000
If you keep this up... I'm cutting ties with...

683
00:30:18,279 --> 00:30:18,799
Xu Rui.

684
00:30:19,799 --> 00:30:20,640
Help me out here.

685
00:30:21,319 --> 00:30:22,559
He and the cousin really aren't a match.

686
00:30:22,559 --> 00:30:24,279
I really don't know how to deal with him anymore.

687
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:27,079
My buddy's own mom,

688
00:30:27,079 --> 00:30:28,000
His own godmother.

689
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:30,039
No need to buy a two-bedroom apartment,

690
00:30:30,279 --> 00:30:31,359
I could dig one out with my toes.

691
00:30:32,319 --> 00:30:32,960
Now you know.

692
00:30:46,759 --> 00:30:48,680
The line's moving faster than I thought.

693
00:30:48,839 --> 00:30:49,480
It really is.

694
00:30:50,839 --> 00:30:51,440
We're almost there.

695
00:30:57,839 --> 00:30:58,480
Xiaocan.

696
00:30:58,799 --> 00:30:59,920
Xiao Tian and I...

697
00:30:59,920 --> 00:31:03,039
...are in line for the Ferris wheel right now.

698
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:04,559
Hurry up and get here.

699
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:05,359
We'll wait for you.

700
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:08,359
Actually, it's my first time at an amusement park.

701
00:31:08,960 --> 00:31:10,720
And my first time riding a Ferris wheel.

702
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:11,720
It's my first time too.

703
00:31:11,839 --> 00:31:12,359
Really?

704
00:31:12,519 --> 00:31:12,960
Really.

705
00:31:13,279 --> 00:31:14,519
If you put it that way...

706
00:31:14,640 --> 00:31:16,160
We should thank Mike.

707
00:31:17,720 --> 00:31:20,400
Mike is actually a really good guy.

708
00:31:21,319 --> 00:31:22,000
But...

709
00:31:23,279 --> 00:31:24,960
I don't like the work he arranges for me.

710
00:31:25,519 --> 00:31:26,680
Especially those...

711
00:31:27,039 --> 00:31:28,599
red carpet events and stuff like that.

712
00:31:29,319 --> 00:31:30,519
Everyone else is a real star.

713
00:31:31,440 --> 00:31:34,240
They can sing, dance, and act.

714
00:31:35,039 --> 00:31:35,880
I can't do anything.

715
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:37,319
I only know how to farm.

716
00:31:37,559 --> 00:31:38,319
Don't say that.

717
00:31:38,319 --> 00:31:40,160
Knowing how to farm is already amazing.

718
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:41,119
That's really impressive.

719
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:45,359
Gui Fang.

720
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:47,480
I'm really happy today.

721
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:48,640
Are you happy today?

722
00:31:51,519 --> 00:31:52,599
I'm happy when I make money.

723
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:54,480
I'm happy when there's a good harvest.

724
00:31:55,240 --> 00:31:57,680
And even happier when it rains back home.

725
00:31:58,599 --> 00:31:59,079
Anyway...

726
00:32:00,039 --> 00:32:01,079
hanging out with you today...

727
00:32:01,519 --> 00:32:02,759
makes me really, really happy.

728
00:32:04,559 --> 00:32:05,480
In the future...

729
00:32:05,480 --> 00:32:08,079
you'll have plenty of happy moments.

730
00:32:08,519 --> 00:32:10,160
Like going to school...

731
00:32:10,279 --> 00:32:10,839
are you happy?

732
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:12,920
Didn't you want to build a dam...

733
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:13,880
for your hometown?

734
00:32:14,319 --> 00:32:16,160
When that dam is finished...

735
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:18,079
the sense of achievement you'll feel...

736
00:32:18,319 --> 00:32:20,400
will make you even happier.

737
00:32:34,480 --> 00:32:35,359
Gui Fang, you're beautiful.

738
00:32:41,839 --> 00:32:43,400
Gui... Gui Fang, l-look.

739
00:32:43,839 --> 00:32:44,319
It's so beautiful.

740
00:32:46,319 --> 00:32:46,839
So beautiful.

741
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:51,119
Alright, alright.

742
00:32:52,359 --> 00:32:53,160
How did you find out?

743
00:32:54,519 --> 00:32:55,240
Auntie told me.

744
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:56,799
My mom really has a big...

745
00:32:57,519 --> 00:32:58,240
Are you okay?

746
00:32:58,519 --> 00:33:00,079
Are you feeling unwell anywhere?

747
00:33:00,079 --> 00:33:00,759
Did you have an accident?

748
00:33:00,960 --> 00:33:01,720
Did something suddenly fall on you?

749
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:02,359
No? Did it?

750
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:03,799
Don't worry.

751
00:33:04,240 --> 00:33:05,119
I haven't told anyone.

752
00:33:05,160 --> 00:33:06,200
I know it's your secret.

753
00:33:06,480 --> 00:33:07,680
No, that's not what I meant. I...

754
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:10,359
Fine, as long as you're okay.

755
00:33:12,319 --> 00:33:12,759
Xu Rui.

756
00:33:13,599 --> 00:33:14,799
There are things I really can't tell you.

757
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:16,279
I'm keeping them from my mom too.

758
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:17,240
Neither of you know.

759
00:33:17,559 --> 00:33:18,640
It's very complicated.

760
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:20,799
I know you want to share the burden.

761
00:33:21,319 --> 00:33:21,759
But I can't let you.

762
00:33:21,759 --> 00:33:23,000
I have to face this alone.

763
00:33:23,519 --> 00:33:24,079
So...

764
00:33:27,240 --> 00:33:27,920
do you understand?

765
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:28,640
Kong Xiaocan.

766
00:33:29,759 --> 00:33:30,720
Today...

767
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:32,680
I just want a clear answer to one thing.

768
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:36,559
Do you want to get back together or not?

769
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:59,119
Xiaocan, Xiao Tian and I are at the front.

770
00:33:59,119 --> 00:33:59,799
Where are you guys?

771
00:33:59,799 --> 00:34:00,799
Why aren't you here yet?

772
00:34:02,000 --> 00:34:02,480
Hello.

773
00:34:02,559 --> 00:34:03,559
Welcome to the Ferris wheel.

774
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:04,359
How many in your party?

775
00:34:05,279 --> 00:34:06,079
Just the two of us.

776
00:34:06,319 --> 00:34:08,079
But we have friends behind us.

777
00:34:08,079 --> 00:34:08,719
They're not here yet.

778
00:34:08,719 --> 00:34:09,000
Right.

779
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:09,880
So, do you want to board now?

780
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:14,159
We waited so long to get here.

781
00:34:15,199 --> 00:34:16,199
Why don't we...

782
00:34:18,039 --> 00:34:18,519
just get on?

783
00:34:18,760 --> 00:34:19,079
Okay.

784
00:34:19,639 --> 00:34:19,960
Please.

785
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:20,800
Thanks.

786
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:27,320
Watch your step.

787
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:23,079
It's so beautiful.

788
00:35:24,519 --> 00:35:25,199
So pretty.

789
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:39,599
The atmosphere is perfect.

790
00:35:40,199 --> 00:35:42,400
The atmosphere isn't quite right.

791
00:35:42,880 --> 00:35:45,440
This kid doesn't have feelings for me, does he?

792
00:35:45,840 --> 00:35:46,480
Cousin...

793
00:35:51,039 --> 00:35:53,159
Why did you have to get on the Ferris wheel with Wei Mingtian?

794
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:54,800
It's so romantic, too.

795
00:35:56,800 --> 00:35:57,800
What a great opportunity.

796
00:35:58,639 --> 00:35:59,880
The timing, the place, and the people are all perfect.

797
00:36:00,440 --> 00:36:01,800
Kong Xiaocan, it's all your fault.

798
00:36:02,000 --> 00:36:03,119
You're just so wishy-washy.

799
00:36:04,719 --> 00:36:05,320
Where are those two?

800
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:08,199
They turned down another path long ago.

801
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:14,480
I knew they still liked each other.

802
00:36:15,079 --> 00:36:15,800
They're definitely getting back together.

803
00:36:16,079 --> 00:36:17,320
It's all within my expectations.

804
00:36:22,119 --> 00:36:23,519
Well, not entirely within my expectations.

805
00:36:25,440 --> 00:36:26,079
In the end,

806
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:28,400
we're the only ones left.

807
00:36:39,400 --> 00:36:39,880
I do.

808
00:36:44,199 --> 00:36:45,000
I want to get back together.

809
00:36:51,119 --> 00:36:51,960
But I can't.

810
00:36:53,599 --> 00:36:54,599
Do you want a beating?

811
00:36:55,960 --> 00:36:56,519
Xu Rui.

812
00:36:57,960 --> 00:36:59,320
You know how much I like you.

813
00:37:00,639 --> 00:37:02,039
But if I get back together with you now,

814
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:04,280
I feel it would be irresponsible.

815
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:06,440
The situation I'm facing right now...

816
00:37:06,960 --> 00:37:07,760
I have no choice.

817
00:37:09,000 --> 00:37:10,320
But I don't want you to misunderstand either.

818
00:37:12,920 --> 00:37:13,559
I hope...

819
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:16,039
we can still be friends.

820
00:37:18,320 --> 00:37:18,840
Is that okay?

821
00:37:22,239 --> 00:37:22,880
Kong Xiaocan.

822
00:37:24,079 --> 00:37:24,719
Let me tell you something.

823
00:37:26,599 --> 00:37:28,159
I can live perfectly fine without you.

824
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:30,360
I know how to make myself happy.

825
00:37:31,039 --> 00:37:32,559
I know there are still many people who love me.

826
00:37:33,800 --> 00:37:34,760
In this past year without you,

827
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:36,239
I've lived a very, very fulfilling life.

828
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:39,480
Also,

829
00:37:42,880 --> 00:37:44,199
I don't need you as a friend.

830
00:37:47,719 --> 00:37:48,519
The mood is set.

831
00:37:49,280 --> 00:37:51,599
Now it's just the two of us.

832
00:37:53,039 --> 00:37:53,599
Come on.

833
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:57,559
It's now or never.

834
00:37:58,039 --> 00:37:58,760
Confess to her.

835
00:37:59,079 --> 00:37:59,480
Gui Fang.

836
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:00,599
I...

837
00:38:01,159 --> 00:38:02,320
I have something to say. Mingtian, listen to me first.

838
00:38:08,239 --> 00:38:09,679
If it's not what I'm thinking,

839
00:38:12,039 --> 00:38:13,119
then I owe you an apology.

840
00:38:14,679 --> 00:38:16,239
But if it is what I'm thinking,

841
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:19,639
then I need to formally say to you:

842
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:23,639
Thank you.

843
00:38:26,039 --> 00:38:27,280
But we can only be friends.

844
00:38:42,599 --> 00:38:44,400
The Big Pendulum was totally worth it.

845
00:38:50,039 --> 00:38:50,920
Riding that Big Pendulum...

846
00:38:51,719 --> 00:38:53,079
brought out your dark circles.

847
00:38:55,880 --> 00:38:56,960
Are you blind?

848
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:58,320
My makeup is smudged.

849
00:38:59,280 --> 00:39:01,039
Can't you tell with those huge colored contacts?

850
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:02,239
I'm not wearing colored contacts.

851
00:39:02,599 --> 00:39:03,519
I was born like this.

852
00:39:03,960 --> 00:39:04,480
Look if you don't believe me.

853
00:39:05,119 --> 00:39:05,719
I'm not looking.

854
00:39:05,800 --> 00:39:06,480
Just look.

855
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:07,519
No.

856
00:39:07,519 --> 00:39:08,719
Seriously, just look.

857
00:39:09,079 --> 00:39:10,000
I'm really not wearing contacts.

858
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:10,880
Get lost. I'm really not.

859
00:39:48,239 --> 00:39:49,800
I know love is beautiful.

860
00:39:51,320 --> 00:39:53,119
But you've fallen for the wrong person.

861
00:39:54,239 --> 00:39:56,119
The person who should be riding alongside you...

862
00:39:56,559 --> 00:39:57,360
is not me.

863
00:40:01,119 --> 00:40:01,880
In this life,

864
00:40:02,320 --> 00:40:05,079
I hope to face my journey solo,

865
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:06,800
walking the world alone.

866
00:40:24,320 --> 00:40:26,400
Is this the world of young people?

867
00:40:30,280 --> 00:40:32,480
Is this the joy of young people?

868
00:40:39,159 --> 00:40:39,840
Go for it!

869
00:40:39,920 --> 00:40:40,800
Go for it!

870
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:42,480
Go for it, children!

871
00:40:43,519 --> 00:40:44,599
Children!

872
00:40:53,119 --> 00:40:54,159
Mom...

873
00:40:54,159 --> 00:40:55,679
Oh, Mom...

874
00:41:01,159 --> 00:41:06,440
Being young is so thrilling!
